# =============================================================================
# .clinerules - Singapore AI Safety Framework Specification
# Path: docs/latex/specs/singapore-ai-safety/.clinerules
# =============================================================================
# This specification defines Singapore-aligned AI governance requirements for
# the SAP-OSS repository, based on IMDA MGF, PDPC, and CSA guidance.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SPECIFICATION OVERVIEW
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose
- Define a single governance baseline across all AI-enabled surfaces in the repository.
- Translate Singapore's AI regulatory frameworks into actionable controls and metrics.
- Provide mathematical models for risk scoring and deployment readiness.
- Document implementation requirements for compliance.

Key Regulatory Sources
- SG-01: IMDA Model AI Governance Framework for Agentic AI (Jan 2026)
- SG-02: IMDA Starter Kit for Testing LLM-Based Applications (Jan 2026)
- SG-03: PDPC Model AI Governance Framework (2nd Ed, Jan 2020)
- SG-04: PDPC Advisory Guidelines on Personal Data in AI (Apr 2024)
- SG-05: IMDA Project Moonshot / AI Verify (May 2024)
- SG-06: Singapore's Approach to AI Governance (Ongoing)
- SG-07: CSA Guidelines on Securing AI Systems (Oct 2024)
- SG-08: CSA Agentic AI Addendum - Consultation Stage (Oct 2025)

